   21: -module(ct_hooks_order_config_suite_SUITE).
   22: 
   23: -suite_defaults([{timetrap, {minutes, 10}}]).
   24: 
   25: %% Note: This directive should only be used in test suites.
   26: -compile([export_all, nowarn_export_all]).
   27: 
   28: -include("ct.hrl").
   29: 
   30: -define(now, ct_test_support:unique_timestamp()).
   31: 
   32: suite() ->
   33:     [{ct_hooks_order, config}].
   34: 
   35: %% Test server callback functions
   36: init_per_suite(Config) ->
   37:     undefined = proplists:get_value(ct_hooks_order, Config),
   38:     [{ips, ?now} | Config].
   39: 
   40: end_per_suite(Config) ->
   41:     undefined = proplists:get_value(ct_hooks_order, Config),
   42:     %% result from end functions is not provided to any other callback
   43:     Config.
   44: 
   45: init_per_testcase(_TestCase, Config) ->
   46:     undefined = proplists:get_value(ct_hooks_order, Config),
   47:     [{ipt, ?now} | Config].
   48: 
   49: end_per_testcase(_TestCase, Config) ->
   50:     undefined = proplists:get_value(ct_hooks_order, Config),
   51:     %% result from end functions is not provided to any other callback
   52:     Config.
   53: 
   54: init_per_group(_GroupName, Config) ->
   55:     undefined = proplists:get_value(ct_hooks_order, Config),
   56:     [{ipg, ?now} | Config].
   57: 
   58: end_per_group(_GroupName, Config) ->
   59:     undefined = proplists:get_value(ct_hooks_order, Config),
   60:     %% result from end functions is not provided to any other callback
   61:     Config.
   62: 
   63: all() ->
   64:     [{group,group1}].
   65: 
   66: groups() ->
   67:     [{group1,[],[test_case]}].
   68: 
   69: test_case(Config) when is_list(Config) ->
   70:     ok.
